overview: Jorge, who is a chemistry student and Paquita's boyfriend, tells the story about his mate, class of 1942 Goyo and his murders. Goyo is having a sentimental relation with Chela, also a student, but at night he strangles prostitutes and buries them in his garden. Jorge and Paquita's romance is broken when a police finds the corpses in the garden at the laboratory.
title: Crimes at North Sea
